//////////////////
html > main tag of website
head > All the links(Css,Js)
     > Except title nothing will be visible 
body > All the content of the website that is visible


Block
> They always start from new line
> Occupies the completed width of screen
> p div h1
Inline
> Start in same line
> Only take the width of content
> span img a


